## Rules

- Every element MUST have a class name
- Use `<header>`, `<main>`, `<footer>`, `<section>`
- Use `<button>` for clicks, `<a>` for links, `<img>` with alt
- Use same container class across sections (e.g., `container-large`)
- Never use emojis - use SVG icons only

